messages: 1fc7e20f37d21669c065017525c88975 (15:35): C'mon buddy, do we have to go through with that? Asl is just a really bad pickup line.
373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:35): Yes, we do. Because only stupid people actually answer it and if you're not stupid you're not the one for me.
373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:36): So I guess we have nothing here that's worth developing.
1fc7e20f37d21669c065017525c88975 (15:36): I really hate to say it, because you'll probably disconnect and your speech indicates a degree of intellect. But sorry, I'm not particuarly stupid.
373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:37): And you're clearly not stupid if you like cake!
373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:37): And how many people have you gone through to get someone who doesn't type lyk thiiis?
373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:38): I play the game where I correctly grammar their statements with proper typing. <_<
373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:38): It can actually be really difficult.
1fc7e20f37d21669c065017525c88975 (15:38): I don't, those people can't be redeemed.
1fc7e20f37d21669c065017525c88975 (15:39): This is an extremely rare trait.
1fc7e20f37d21669c065017525c88975 (15:39): I can't help but be in extreme astonishment.
373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:39): Since we won't meet face to face, just call me that to entertain me.
373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:39): And I'll call you whatever you want as long as it doesn't involve the word "master" because that's ended badly before.
373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:40): I shall call you Mr Bubbles.
1fc7e20f37d21669c065017525c88975 (15:40): But I want you to whisper it in my ear.
373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:40): And you're sure you don't wish to play the grammar correction game?

373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:40): tha ciity eyy..hmm..wif u n rushyy .. hmmm..i duno ey
haha narr of course mahnn, biin missin yall boiiz ey
ye holla at me one tyme ey, u gt my digits ey
373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:41): If I'm going to whisper it in your ear, I'll call you Sweet Nothings.
1fc7e20f37d21669c065017525c88975 (15:41): So you're copying and pasting all this.
1fc7e20f37d21669c065017525c88975 (15:41): I assume you've had this conversation before, with someone else?
1fc7e20f37d21669c065017525c88975 (15:41): I can deal with that, God.
373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:41): Oh no, I haven't found someone to play it with yet.
1fc7e20f37d21669c065017525c88975 (15:42): I can't say I want to play at the moment, I'm afraid.
1fc7e20f37d21669c065017525c88975 (15:42): What brought you to Omegle, God?
1fc7e20f37d21669c065017525c88975 (15:43): Sheer boredom, and desire to affirm my hatred for humanity.
373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:43): I hope you have achieved it.
373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:43): And I hope I have slightly redeemed it.
373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:43): For that's what I'm meant to do, I think.
1fc7e20f37d21669c065017525c88975 (15:44): Well, you are God, I suppose.
373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:44): Anyway, farewell Mr Bubbles. May your adventures be advantageous to you.
373afe0052f0aef041f87811f1d21361 (15:44): I will never forget this, Mr Bubbles.
1fc7e20f37d21669c065017525c88975 (15:44): Well, if you desire to depart,
1fc7e20f37d21669c065017525c88975 (15:45): It took me forty people to get to you.
